- EpochBarrier synchronization
- Symbol validity windows tied to epochs
- Expiration: cancellation + cleanup

## Test Areas
- Basic epoch creation/advance
- Barrier all-or-nothing behavior
- Expired epoch triggers cancellations
- Determinism with lab runtime
- Boundary cases: overflow, zero-duration, nested epochs

## Acceptance
- Deterministic lab tests for all scenarios
- Invariants preserved (no leaks, quiescence on close)
- Trace output on failures
